{"tid":1534620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔係怠慢左行動，係怠慢左宣傳，而家活動太多太散，好多活動都係臨尾先知，唔上連登更加唔會知","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:27:03.000Z","uid":31215,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20ca9263357283cba5a9c24a46ba29fc81cf4078","tid":1534620,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:33.000Z","msg":"SSP 遊行嗰期，有聲音檢討一週二行係咪太密，減少左人數<br />\n之後冇減活動之餘，仲有越黎越密傾向<br />\n變成一日二至三個活動<br />\n閒日都有排活動<br />\n仲未計即興突發野<br />\n<br />\n所以點解好似行動post少左咁多<br />\n因為太多太散<br />\n都唔知推邊個<br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得69遊行<br />\n連登仔用左幾多日黎推<br />\n上網吹雞做嘅活動，e.g. 派傳單，都係為左宣傳69<br />\n而往後D活動因為夠聚焦，蘋果甚至可以幫手出頭條吹雞<br />\n<br />\n而家呢個情況同冇大台都有D關係，大家都各有各發起，各有各宣傳，各有各去<br />\n本身其實問題不大，當打遊擊<br />\n但如果大家想有返個不得不去嘅氣勢，係咪要有共識鎖定一啲重心項目，然後全部人幫手推、幫手宣傳、幫手去<br />\n而家做到聚焦效果嘅得民陣嗰D活動<br />\n網民搞嗰D始終都係太散<br />\n<br />\n有心水嘅巴打<br />\n你留言講個你覺得係未來一至兩週嘅重點項目，最好有埋文宣，我就努力宣傳"},{"pid":"e8dc5fdc62a617dbcc91d0fdbe76bc5766eb4d16","tid":1534620,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f020ab4020be25f741fcf986d9ad539a958e3022","tid":1534620,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57015fb24223246e3793812d49ed563c85abd7c","tid":1534620,"uid":300937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:19:55.000Z","msg":"宣傳夠唔夠真係好影響成效 所以大家要集中火力谷多啲至係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9692005ff54237428dba442bfad3fe913d3159ec","tid":1534620,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:27.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n